{"tid":1670285,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"撐加泰時請確保知道自己做緊乜","createTime":"2019-10-23T02:57:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T03:15:08.000Z","uid":59518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9e7d72f3605364cbb2909c6fd24308c12bc81ab9","tid":1670285,"uid":59518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:57:21.000Z","msg":"我唔係幾肯定以依家既主題 <br />\n真係適合由香港人發起集會 仲要成為反送中引起既抗爭其中一項？<br />\n<br />\n你係要支持加泰獨立？<br />\n你係要用香港人民眾既身份去讉責人地個政府？<br />\n你係要將一個歐盟政權同中共放埋一齊？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WR4TqmK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWR4TqmK.jpg&h=61b6a28c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ipAOYGL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FipAOYGL.jpg&h=a277ba6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A5FWn8K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA5FWn8K.jpg&h=33b5ae66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想請教 6月到依家 <br />\n歐美有冇試過有一個由當地人發起既大型集會<br />\n主題係 五大訴求 缺一不可／讉責香港政府 ／<br />\n支持一國兩制／支持香港獨立 etc.<br />\n呢類直接關乎人地國家事務既topic?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n定你係要宣揚同支持普世價值 抗警暴 抗極權？咁點解唔改集會主題<br />\n<br />\n點解世界咁多示威你淨係撐加泰？係咪因為巴塞係加泰首府呀<br />\n點解9.29全球集會要叫抗極權赤納綷？唔叫全球支援香港抗共？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又或者你係要連結港獨議題既<br />\n依家又係一個打開口牌時間？"},{"pid":"e065beb23877c6ee68037ad40ecc883c60437d7c","tid":1670285,"uid":171866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:00:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">加泰post不推文回覆，各位要冷處理</span></strong></span><span style=\"color: red;\"></span>"},{"pid":"c3f2f1c78e013dbef7bf83efc254687193674c5f","tid":1670285,"uid":59518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e065beb23877c6ee68037ad40ecc883c60437d7c","tid":1670285,"uid":171866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:00:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">加泰post不推文回覆，各位